## Thứ tự triển khai

### Phase 1: Core Foundation
1. [types.ts](file:///Users/tmduoc/working/coding/learning/saleor-dashboard/src/components/ConditionalFilter/types.ts) — Tất cả type definitions
2. [constants.ts](file:///Users/tmduoc/working/coding/learning/saleor-dashboard/src/components/ConditionalFilter/constants.ts) — Default operators per field type
3. `helpers/operators.ts` — Operator → query param mapping
4. `helpers/query-builder.ts` — Build REST query params
5. `helpers/validators.ts` — Validate filter rows
6. `helpers/serializer.ts` — Serialize/deserialize to URL

### Phase 2: State & Hooks
7. `hooks/use-filter-state.ts` — CRUD state management
8. `hooks/use-filter-url-sync.ts` — URL synchronization
9. `hooks/use-filter-options.ts` — Dynamic option fetching
10. `provider/filter-context.ts` + `filter-provider.tsx` — Context

### Phase 3: UI Components
11. `ui/field-select.tsx` — Field combobox (shadcn Command)
12. `ui/operator-select.tsx` — Operator select
13. `ui/value-input.tsx` — Dynamic value input renderer
14. `ui/filter-row.tsx` — Compose 1 row
15. `ui/filter-footer.tsx` — Action buttons
16. `ui/filter-root.tsx` — Main container
17. `ui/filter-badge.tsx` — Active filter count

### Phase 4: Testing & Polish
18. Unit tests cho query-builder, validators, serializer
19. Integration test cho full filter flow
20. Storybook hoặc demo page

